ED_DecisionText:
At its 76th meeting, on 24 December 2017, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Fifth Committee,  took note of the report of the Secretary-General on the United Nations Office for Partnerships.


(See A/72/668, para. 9; A/72/PV.76)
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/72/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
